## Overview

The **LiveChat API Plugin** allows seamless integration with the LiveChat platform, enabling users to manage chats, initiate new conversations, and retrieve a list of ongoing or past chats. This plugin provides essential tools for real-time customer support and engagement. Authentication is handled using OAuth2 or API tokens to ensure secure access to LiveChat resources.

